<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//APACHE//DTD Documentation V2.0//EN" "http://forrest.apache.org/dtd/document-v20.dtd">

<document>
  <header>
    <title>templeton/status </title>
  </header>

  <body>
  <section>
   <title>Description</title>
    <p>Returns the current status of the Templeton server.  
       Useful for heartbeat monitoring.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
   <title>Usage</title>
    <p><code>GET /v1/templeton/status.json</code></p>
  </section>

  <section>
   <title>Parameters</title>
    <p>Only the <a href="index.html#Standard+Parameters">standard parameters</a>
       are accepted.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
   <title>Results</title>
    <p>Returns the JSON object:</p>
    <p><code> {"status": MESSAGE} </code></p>
    <p>Where MESSAGE is a string similar to "ok".</p>
  </section>
 </body>
</document>
